WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.000
POV: the gripper starts with the cube area in view.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.000
It sweeps across the workspace while searching for the target.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:18.000
The gripper approaches the wrong pickup line.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:25.000
The cube fills the view as the fingers close.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:32.000
The arm lifts and carries the cube away.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:41.000
It continues repositioning with the object near the gripper.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:50.534
The arm finishes the attempt, showing the incorrect red-run outcome.
